  "parent_id": "4204511237",
  "children": [],
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "When update GHS from 202114 to 202314 version.  with compile option -ONone , program flied and running in dead address."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/202314%20version%20GHS%20update/image-2024-7-5_18-1-58.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/202314 version GHS update/image-2024-7-5_18-1-58.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Reason:"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Normal case:  with -ODebug option"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/202314%20version%20GHS%20update/image-2024-7-5_18-2-26.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/202314 version GHS update/image-2024-7-5_18-2-26.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Startup_MbistTriggerNDST()  is a inline function and not  use a4 register."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/202314%20version%20GHS%20update/image-2024-7-5_18-4-28.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/202314 version GHS update/image-2024-7-5_18-4-28.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Error Case:"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "with -ONone option"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Startup_MbistTriggerNDST()  use a4 register and  Startup_MbistCheckResutl() --the 2ed function don't recalucate a4 address."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "These 2 points result in the issue."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/202314%20version%20GHS%20update/image-2024-7-5_18-3-10.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/202314 version GHS update/image-2024-7-5_18-3-10.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "------------------------------------------------------------------------"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Maybe Compiler think no one should change a4 register when use pseudo jump. So a4 won't change between 1st and 2ed function."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "There is a macro MBIST_USE_JUMP_FUN_CALL to use pseudo jump OR inline . Only pseudo jump can cause this issue"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Below picture MBIST_USE_JUMP_FUN_CALL is 0u (inline function )."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/202314%20version%20GHS%20update/image-2024-7-5_18-30-0.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/202314 version GHS update/image-2024-7-5_18-30-0.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/202314%20version%20GHS%20update/image-2024-7-5_18-32-8.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/202314 version GHS update/image-2024-7-5_18-32-8.png"
    }
  ],
